    • Method Detail

      • deserialize

        OobIncomingMessage deserialize(java.lang.String mimeType,
                               byte[] content)
                        throws OobException
        Parse incoming message from byte array into OobIncomingMessage object. The following fields will be handled by the SDK. Application developer only needs to provided the getter inside your custom message object.
        • messageId
        • providerId
        • acknowledgmentRequested
        • expirationDate
        Parameters:
        mimeType - MIME type of the message.
        content - content of the message in byte array.
        Returns:
        deserialize message object.
        Throws:
        OobException - Exception thrown while parsing fails.
